      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept good-condition car that presents nicely overall. The exterior and interior show normal light wear consistent with age and use, but it remains an honest, solid example that should satisfy a buyer looking for a nice driver rather than a fully restored or show-level car. Expect a vehicle that has been cared for, looks good in person, and still has a few minor cosmetic signs of use here and there.",
