      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$4,900 - Budget-friendly project car for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. This one is in poor condition and will need significant work; it\u2019s best suited for a buyer who wants a repair project, restoration candidate, or possible parts car. It has clear age, wear, and cosmetic issues, so please come with realistic expectations, but for the right person it could still be a worthwhile opportunity at an affordable price.",
