    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest value and a smart opportunity for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered in budget-friendly condition and is best suited for someone looking for affordable transportation, a project, or a practical spare. It presents a straightforward chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price, backed by clear, transparent advertising from a trusted seller. If you want low upfront cost and solid potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and can make a great budget runabout, first car, or weekend project for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC. If you\u2019re after cheap, usable transport without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look. Priced fairly and ready to go to its next home.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, usable car with cosmetic wear and signs of age, but it still offers a strong foundation for a daily driver, backup car, or weekend project. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission does its job, and the chassis feels mechanically straightforward with plenty of life left for the next owner willing to sort the small stuff. Not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable car with good utility and solid potential for someone who values function over finish.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car or project. Priced to sell fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, lived-in charm that\u2019s getting harder to find\u2014a dependable old companion with plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates character, needs affordable wheels, or wants a practical project with real everyday potential. Turn the key, imagine the possibilities, and enjoy a vehicle that offers usefulness, personality, and value without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation without unnecessary frills. It shows its age and would benefit from some TLC, but it remains a straightforward, usable option for a value-focused buyer. A great fit for a commuter, first-time buyer, or someone looking for an inexpensive project with room to make it their own.",
      "price": 4950.0,
